3.Data Preprocessing¶

owercase , tokenization , removing special character , removing stop words and punctuation , stemming

In [42]:
from nltk.corpus import stopwords
import string
from nltk.stem.porter import PorterStemmer
ps = PorterStemmer()
In [43]:
def transform(text):
    text = text.lower() #lower
    text = nltk.word_tokenize(text)  #token
    
    y = [] #removing special character
    for i in text:
        if i.isalnum():
            y.append(i)
            
    text = y[:]
    y.clear()
    
    for i in text:  ## removing stopwords and punctuation
        if i not in stopwords.words('english') and i not in string.punctuation:
            y.append(i)
            
    text = y[:]
    y.clear()
    
    for i in text:  ## stemming
        y.append(ps.stem(i))
        
    return " ".join(y)
